Question

Delete a node in a linked list when only that node is given
(head access nahi hai)

â­ Trick / Logic

Given node ke next node ka data lo

Us data ko current node me copy kar do

Current node ka next pointer
â†’ next ke next pe point kara do

âœï¸ Steps
node->val = node->next->val;
node->next = node->next->next;

ğŸ§  Why this works?

Tum actually given node ko delete nahi kar rahe

Tum uske next node ko delete kar rahe ho

Aur uska data current node me copy kar rahe ho

